<subSubSection id="C337088DF779B138B182FD4C37A94057" pageId="12" pageNumber="533" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B925B06F779B138B182FD4C37A94057" blockId="12.[151,1437,475,789]" pageId="12" pageNumber="533">
COMMENTS: The 
<typeStatus id="5496E5A4F779B138B0C1FD4C338E418F" box="[388,439,691,717]" pageId="12" pageNumber="533">type</typeStatus>
locality matches journal entries for this date and place. On 1 November Wahlberg camped at uMhlatuze River, moving to uMlalazi River on 2 November. On 6 November he moved to the uMatikulu River, and then to Thukela River mouth on 7 November and back to uMlalazi River on 10 November.
</paragraph>
